OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,FBafta has apologised "unreservedly" to
OL,7,Fthe black and disability communities
OL,8,Fafter a racial slur was broadcast
OL,9,Fduring its 2026 film awards.
OL,11,FThe arts charity added that an
OL,12,Findependent review found "a number of
OL,13,Fstructural weaknesses" in its planning
OL,14,Ffor the event.
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@cO]tD@ZOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
