OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,FDuring the ceremony in February,
OL,7,Fdisability campaigner John Davidson,
OL,8,Fwho has Tourette's, could be heard
OL,9,Fshouting a racial slur as Sinners
OL,10,Fstars Michael B Jordan and Delroy
OL,11,FLindo presented the award for special
OL,12,Fvisual effects.
OL,14,FFollowing the incident, the Bafta
OL,15,Fboard commissioned an independent
OL,16,Freview by RISE Associates to examine
OL,17,Fwhat happened and what must change
OL,18,Fmoving forward, the charity's
OL,19,Fstatement said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,F"The review, which is now complete,
OL,7,Fidentified a number of structural
OL,8,Fweaknesses in BAFTA's planning,
OL,9,Fescalation procedures and crisis
OL,10,Fcoordination arrangements.
OL,12,F"However, it did not find evidence of
OL,13,Fmalicious intent on the part of those
OL,14,Finvolved in delivering the event. We
OL,15,Faccept its conclusions in full.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,F"We apologise unreservedly to the
OL,7,FBlack community, for whom the racist
OL,8,Flanguage used carries real pain,
OL,9,Fbrutality, and trauma; to the
OL,10,Fdisability community, including people
OL,11,Fwith Tourette Syndrome, for whom this
OL,12,Fincident has led to unfair judgement,
OL,13,Fstigma, and distress," Bafta said.
OL,15,FThe charity also said it apologises to
OL,16,F"all our members, guests at the
OL,17,Fceremony and those watching at home",
OL,18,Fadding: "What was supposed to be a
OL,19,Fmoment of celebration was diminished
OL,20,Fand overshadowed.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,F"We have written to those directly
OL,7,Fimpacted on the night to apologise.
OL,9,F"The review is clear that while this
OL,10,Fwas not a failure of intent, BAFTA's
OL,11,Fplanning and processes have not kept
OL,12,Fpace with its diversity and inclusion
OL,13,Fgoals.
OL,15,F"We did not adequately anticipate or
OL,16,Ffully prepare for the impact of such
OL,17,Fan incident in a live event
OL,18,Fenvironment and as a result our duty
OL,19,Fof care to everyone at the ceremony
OL,20,Fand watching at home fell short."
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
