OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,FThe academy said work is under way as
OL,7,Fa "priority" to address the areas of
OL,8,Fimprovement specified in the review,
OL,9,Fcarried out by Rise Associates, to
OL,10,F"reduce the risk of this happening
OL,11,Fagain".
OL,13,FIt comes after an investigation found
OL,14,Fthe BBC breached its editorial
OL,15,Fstandards when it broadcast the slur.
OL,26,@oD@COUoD@LO]rD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
