OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775823078
OL,3,CBafta apologises 'unreservedly' after
OL,4,Cindependent review into racial slur
OL,6,FThe ECU added the delay was "a serious
OL,7,Fmistake, because there could be no
OL,8,Fcertainty that the word would be
OL,9,Finaudible to all viewers".
OL,11,FThe report confirmed the BBC's chief
OL,12,Fcontent officer has sent letters of
OL,13,Fapology to Lindo, Jordan and Davidson.
